<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>SPK {{doc.number}}</title>
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Calibri', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #111;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  {{#if company.letterheadUrl}}
  .letterhead-bg {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 210mm; height: 297mm;
    z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
  }
  {{/if}}

  table.page-layout { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  table.page-layout > thead > tr > td.page-header-spacer {
    height: {{#if company.letterheadUrl}}38mm{{else}}18mm{{/if}};
    padding: 0; border: 0;
  }
  table.page-layout > tfoot > tr > td.page-footer-spacer {
    height: {{#if company.letterheadUrl}}45mm{{else}}22mm{{/if}};
    padding: 0; border: 0;
  }
  table.page-layout > tbody > tr > td.page-content {
    padding: 0 22mm;
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .fallback-header {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12pt;
    border-bottom: 2pt solid {{theme.primary}};
    padding-bottom: 8pt; margin-bottom: 14pt;
  }
  .fallback-header .logo { width: 60pt; height: 60pt; object-fit: contain; }
  .fallback-header .company-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 16pt; color: {{theme.primary}}; letter-spacing: .5pt; }
  .fallback-header .company-addr { font-size: 9.5pt; color: #333; margin-top: 2pt; line-height: 1.35; }

  /* Title SPK */
  .spk-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14pt;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: underline;
    letter-spacing: 1.5pt;
    margin: 6pt 0 14pt 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Header table — "No : ..." style */
  table.spk-header { font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 12pt; }
  table.spk-header td { padding: 1pt 0; vertical-align: top; }
  table.spk-header td.k { width: 130pt; font-weight: 600; }
  table.spk-header td.s { width: 12pt; }

  /* Paragraf utama */
  .main-paragraph {
    text-align: justify;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 8pt 0 6pt 0;
  }

  /* List spesifikasi — table 2 kolom (no. urut + deskripsi) untuk penataan rapi & sejajar.
     Nomor di kolom sempit di kiri, deskripsi mengisi sisa lebar. Kalau deskripsi wrap,
     baris berikutnya rata dengan baris pertama (bukan dengan nomor). */
  table.spec-list {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 8pt 0 12pt 24pt;     /* tab-indent dari kiri */
    font-size: 11pt;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  table.spec-list td {
    vertical-align: top;
    padding: 3pt 4pt;
  }
  table.spec-list td.no-col {
    width: 26pt;
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 8pt;
    color: {{theme.primaryDark}};
    font-weight: 700;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  table.spec-list td.desc-col {
    text-align: left;
  }
  /* Unit text — tampil di-bawah deskripsi, abu-abu kecil (sama style dengan RAB preview) */
  table.spec-list td.desc-col .item-unit {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1pt;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #6b7280;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  /* Striping zebra tipis biar enak dibaca */
  table.spec-list tbody tr:nth-child(odd) td { background: {{theme.primarySubtle}}; }
  /* Header kategori — full-width, bold, kontras */
  table.spec-list tr.cat-row td {
    background: {{theme.primary}} !important;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10pt;
    letter-spacing: .4pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4pt 8pt;
    margin-top: 6pt;
  }

  /* Catatan dengan prefix "#" */
  .hash-notes {
    margin: 8pt 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .hash-notes .hash-line {
    margin-bottom: 2pt;
  }

  /* Bullet pembayaran "•" */
  .bullet-list {
    margin: 8pt 0;
    padding-left: 18pt;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .bullet-list li {
    margin-bottom: 4pt;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  /* Bank list */
  .bank-block {
    margin: 8pt 0;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .bank-block .bank-line {
    margin-left: 24pt;
    margin-bottom: 2pt;
  }

  /* Closing & signature */
  .closing-line { margin-top: 10pt; line-height: 1.55; }
  .sign-date { margin-top: 14pt; font-weight: 600; }

  .signature-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 30pt;
    margin-top: 18pt;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .signature-row .block {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 200pt;
  }
  .signature-row .role {
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4pt;
  }
  .signature-row .sign-area {
    position: relative;
    height: 80pt;
    margin: 4pt 0;
  }
  .signature-row .sign-image {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    max-height: 80pt; max-width: 180pt; z-index: 2;
  }
  .signature-row .stamp-image {
    position: absolute; top: 8pt; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-72%);
    max-height: 80pt; max-width: 110pt;
    opacity: 0.85; z-index: 1;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }
  .signature-row .materai {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #555;
    padding: 26pt 0;
  }
  .signature-row .name {
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
    margin-top: 4pt;
  }

  .end-spacer { height: 36pt; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

{{#if company.letterheadUrl}}
<img class="letterhead-bg" src="{{company.letterheadUrl}}" alt="" />
{{/if}}

<table class="page-layout">
  <thead><tr><td class="page-header-spacer"></td></tr></thead>
  <tfoot><tr><td class="page-footer-spacer"></td></tr></tfoot>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td class="page-content">

<div class="content">

  {{#unless company.letterheadUrl}}
  <div class="fallback-header">
    {{#if company.logoUrl}}<img class="logo" src="{{company.logoUrl}}" />{{/if}}
    <div>
      <div class="company-name">{{company.name}}</div>
      <div class="company-addr">
        {{company.address}}<br/>
        {{#if company.phone}}Telp: {{company.phone}}{{/if}}{{#if company.email}} &bull; {{company.email}}{{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/unless}}

  <div class="spk-title">Surat Perintah Kerja</div>

  {{!-- Header info: No, Hal, Nama Perusahaan, Penanggung Jawab, dst --}}
  <table class="spk-header">
    <tr><td class="k">No</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{doc.number}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="k">Hal</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{doc.variantLabel}}</td></tr>
    {{#if client.company}}<tr><td class="k">Nama Perusahaan</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{client.company}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    <tr><td class="k">Penanggung Jawab</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{client.name}}</td></tr>
    {{#if client.position}}<tr><td class="k">Jabatan</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{client.position}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    {{#if client.phone}}<tr><td class="k">No. Telp kantor</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{client.phone}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    {{#if client.address}}<tr><td class="k">Alamat</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{client.address}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    {{#if project.name}}<tr><td class="k">Event</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{project.name}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    {{#if project.location}}<tr><td class="k">Tempat</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{project.location}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
    {{#if project.dateRange}}<tr><td class="k">Tanggal Event</td><td class="s">:</td><td>{{project.dateRange}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
  </table>

  {{!-- Paragraf utama: "Dengan ini memberikan pekerjaan kepada..." --}}
  <p class="main-paragraph">
    Dengan ini memberikan pekerjaan kepada <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> untuk pemasangan {{lowercase doc.variantLabel}}{{#if project.name}} pada Event <strong>{{project.name}}</strong>{{/if}}{{#if project.dateRange}} tanggal <strong>{{project.dateRange}}</strong>{{/if}}{{#if project.location}} di <strong>{{project.location}}</strong>{{/if}}, yaitu sebesar <strong>{{totals.total}}</strong>{{#if spk.exclTax}} exclude PPN dan PPH{{else}} sudah termasuk PPN {{totals.taxRate}}%{{/if}}, dengan spesifikasi sebagai berikut:
  </p>

  {{!-- Standalone Terbilang line — lebih mencolok daripada inline parentheses --}}
  {{#if totals.totalTerbilang}}
  <div class="terbilang-block" style="margin: 4pt 0 8pt 0; font-style: italic; font-size: 11pt; padding: 4pt 8pt; border-left: 3pt solid {{theme.primary}}; background: {{theme.primarySubtle}};">
    <strong>Terbilang:</strong> <strong style="color: {{theme.primaryDark}};">{{totals.totalTerbilang}}</strong>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{!-- List spesifikasi — table 2 kolom (no. urut + deskripsi). Nomor urut consecutive
       di seluruh list (1, 2, 3, ...) supaya enak dibaca, bukan reset per kategori. --}}
  <table class="spec-list">
    <tbody>
      {{#each spk.specItems}}
        {{#if this.isCategoryHeader}}
        <tr class="cat-row"><td colspan="2">{{this.label}}</td></tr>
        {{else}}
        <tr>
          <td class="no-col">{{this.no}}.</td>
          <td class="desc-col">
            {{this.description}}
            {{#if this.quantity}}<span class="item-unit">{{this.quantity}}</span>{{/if}}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  {{!-- Specifications section — render kalau di-set di Quotation (PDF Nukahiji style).
       Group dengan judul (Booth/Stage/Totem) + bullet checkmarks. --}}
  {{#if specifications}}
  <div style="margin: 8pt 0 10pt 0;">
    <div style="font-weight: 700; color: {{theme.primary}}; margin-bottom: 4pt; font-size: 11pt; border-bottom: 0.5pt solid {{theme.primary}}; padding-bottom: 2pt;">
      Spesifikasi
    </div>
    {{#each specifications}}
    <div style="margin-top: 4pt;">
      {{#if this.title}}
      <div style="font-weight: 700; color: {{../theme.primaryDark}}; margin-bottom: 2pt; font-size: 10.5pt;">▪ {{this.title}}</div>
      {{/if}}
      <ul style="margin: 0 0 6pt 24pt; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 10.5pt;">
        {{#each this.items}}<li>✓ {{this}}</li>{{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{!-- Catatan dengan prefix "#" — dari brand disclaimer (split per baris) --}}
  {{#if brandTexts.disclaimer}}
  <div class="hash-notes" style="white-space: pre-line;">{{spk.disclaimerHashed}}</div>
  {{/if}}

  {{!-- Bullet pembayaran — kalau ada paymentSchedule custom, pakai itu. Else fallback ke DP+Pelunasan default. --}}
  <ul class="bullet-list">
    {{#if paymentSchedule}}
      {{#each paymentSchedule}}
      <li>
        <strong>{{this.label}} {{this.percent}}%</strong> dari nominal kontrak sebesar <strong>{{this.amountFormatted}}</strong> ({{this.amountTerbilang}}){{#if @first}} dibayarkan pada saat surat perintah kerja ini ditandatangani{{else}}{{#if @last}} sebagai pelunasan akhir{{else}} dibayarkan secara bertahap{{/if}}{{/if}}.
      </li>
      {{/each}}
    {{else}}
      <li>DP {{payment.dpPercent}}% dari nominal kontrak atau sebesar <strong>{{payment.dpAmount}}</strong> ({{payment.dpAmountTerbilang}}) dibayarkan pada saat surat perintah kerja ini ditandatangani.</li>
      <li>Pelunasan sebesar <strong>{{payment.pelunasan}}</strong> ({{payment.pelunasanTerbilang}}) dibayarkan pada saat booth berdiri{{#if spk.paymentDeadlineFormatted}} atau selambat-lambatnya pada tanggal <strong>{{spk.paymentDeadlineFormatted}}</strong>{{/if}}.</li>
    {{/if}}
    <li>Surat Perintah Kerja tidak bisa dibatalkan. Apabila terjadi pembatalan, maka pembatalan akan dikenakan biaya 50% dari total harga. Dan dibayarkan maksimal 1 (satu) minggu dari pembatalan surat perintah kerja. Pembayaran DP yang sudah kami terima tidak dapat dikembalikan.</li>
    <li>Pembatalan Surat Perintah Kerja disampaikan secara tertulis.</li>
  </ul>

  {{#if payment.banks.length}}
  <div class="bank-block">
    Pembayaran dapat ditransfer ke rekening :
    {{#each payment.banks}}
    <div class="bank-line">{{this.bankName}} <strong>{{this.accountNumber}}</strong> an. {{this.accountOwner}}</div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <div class="closing-line">
    Demikian Surat Perintah Kerja dibuat dan ditandatangani atas kesepakatan bersama :
  </div>

  <div class="sign-date">{{doc.dateFormatted}}</div>

  {{!-- TTD: Vendor (kiri) | Klien (kanan) --}}
  <div class="signature-row">
    <div class="block">
      <div class="role">{{company.name}}</div>
      <div class="sign-area">
        {{#if signedBy.stampUrl}}<img class="stamp-image" src="{{signedBy.stampUrl}}" alt="Stempel" />{{/if}}
        {{#if signedBy.signatureUrl}}<img class="sign-image" src="{{signedBy.signatureUrl}}" alt="Tanda Tangan" />{{/if}}
      </div>
      <div class="name">{{signedBy.name}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="block">
      <div class="role">{{#if client.company}}{{client.company}}{{else}}{{client.name}}{{/if}}</div>
      <div class="sign-area">
        <div class="materai">Materai 10000</div>
      </div>
      <div class="name">{{client.name}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="end-spacer"></div>

</div>

    </td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

</body>
</html>
